Output level 1.1/ Hydrometric monitoring network outdated and inadequate 1.2/ 0 hazard and risk maps, flood plain zoning and MH vulnerability and risk assessments 1.3/ Level= 0 1.4/ Level= 0 2.1/ Level = 0 2.2/ MHEWS does not exist: institutional responsibilities and communication protocols for EWS, climate and disaster risk management are not properly defined. FFEWS is available only for the Rioni river basin. 2.3/ 0% 3.1/ 0 (“last-mile” EWS communications not practiced in Georgia) 3.2/ Baseline to be established in project Year 1 through 1st phase of community impact evaluation programme 3.3/ 0 3.4/ Baseline to be established in Year 1 of the project through KAP Survey

