a/ Procurement and installation of a telecommunication system; 
b/ Procurement and operationalization of HPC; 
c/ Observation equipment for 9 river basins (7 Automatic meteorological stations, 50 Automatic meteorological posts, 26 Automatic hydrological posts, 6 Snow Measurement equipment)
d/ Procurement of 15 Agrometeorological Stations
