a/ Develop a Unified methodology for multi-hazard mapping & risk assessment. 
b/ Collection of LiDAR data
c/ Development of hazard maps and risk profiles for 3 river basins: Supsa, Natanebi, Kintrishi. 
e/ Collection of hydro-meteorological and geological field data and processing of historical data for hazard-mapping for next set of basins
1.3/
a/ Upgrading the GIS-based socio-economic model;
b/ Socio-economic assessment for three river basins (Supsa, Natanebi, Kintrishi) completed.
