a/ International technical advice delivered to NEA on Enhancing meteorological forecasting capacities;
b/International technical advice delivered to NEA on Enhancing capacity to integrate new data source into forecasting platform;
c/International technical advice delivered to NEA on Expanding flood forecasting platform (upgrading Rioni flood forecasting platform).
